.Sh NAME
.Nm pv
.Nd paravirtual device tree root
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "pv* at pvbus?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
driver is used on virtual machines that are running on hypervisors.
It provides a pseudo-bus for all paravirtual devices that do not
attach to a well-known bus like
.Xr pci 4 .
